name: Google Search Dark Theme [V1.4.19]
description: A Dark Theme for Google Search/Images for when you want to work in the dark. Check out my other Google Dark Themes: Dark Theme for Google Docs Dark Theme for Google Translate Google Classroom Dark Theme Google Drive Dark Theme Feel free to leave some feedback down below!

user.name: Lekrkoekj
user.about:
Hi I'm Lekrkoekj! 
I mostly make Dark Themes for a lot of sites on here. If you like any of my styles,  be sure to give feedback on them.
